name: Insurance Consultants Inc
overview:
Founded over 30 years ago, Wenzel & Associates Insurance in association with Insurance Consultants, Inc offers both personal and commercial insurance coverage. We are the premier insurance agency in the St. Louis, Mo. and surrounding counties area. Integrity and reputation is all we own that is why we are a part of the Better Business Bureau, Independent Insurance Agency & Brokers of America, the Insurance Information Institute and Trusted Choice.

Our specialties lie in the Commercial side of the Insurance business and the majority of our portfolio is found in Real Estate, Property Management and Construction Management insurance offerings.

We provide a variety of coverage including; AAA, Acuity, Allied, America First, Am Trust, Columbia Insurance, Fireman&#8217;s Fund, The Hartford, State Auto, Travelers, Zurich, Ciba and others. Please feel free to reach out to us or call at 636.394.9070

Specialties

BOP, Worker’s Compensation, Home and Auto Insurance Packages, Umbrellas, General Liability, Business Insurance, D&O, MultiFamily Policies, Builder’s Risk, Dwelling Policies, Renter’s Insurance, General Liability
